page loads. ryu is standing still
hover mouse over > shifts to his ready pose
  stop hovering > back to still
mouse down > leans forward and throws a 'hadouken gif'
  hadouken transitions left - right across screen and disappears
    plays hadouken.mp3
  ryu remains in that pose until mouse up
  mouse up > ryu to ready pose
'x' key down > ryu in 'ryu-cool.gif'
  'x' key up > back to ready pose
  plays 'with them' mp3
